\section{Warning}{
   It is not allowed to read simultaneously portion of bands and portion of lines from file, \emph{e.g.},
\preformatted{
   x <- open_envi(fname)
   y <- x[2:3,10:20]
   close(x)
}
Such brunch is not implemented in code. You use one of the followed tricks:
\preformatted{
   x <- open_envi(fname)
   y <- x[2:3][,20:30]
   close(x)
}
or
\preformatted{
   x <- open_envi(fname)
   y <- x[,20:30][2:3]
   close(x)
}
}

